    "How should knowledge work and knowledge flows be redesigned to harness GenAI capabilities?",
    "Which domains and use cases benefit from the integration of GenAI and in which areas might its use be counterproductive?",
    "To realize benefit of GenAI while mitigating its risks, organizations may use some techniques including reinforcement learning with human feedback (RLHF)(Griffin et al.",
    "2013; Saunders et al.,2017) and tools that provide feedback to GenAI models (e.g., argilla.io) to exert more control over the knowledge generated by these tools.",
